revision.text:
'''Dr. Mohamed Munavvar''' was born in the island of [[Meedhoo (Seenu Atoll)]] in [[Maldives]]. He was former Attorney General of [[Maldives]].
==Early and personal life== Munavvar has two daughters. ==Educational background== Munavvar completed his secondary education in [[English Preparatory and Secondary School]] in Male'. ==Political career== He was former MP of [[Addu]] Atoll constituency. {{start box}}
