[[dv:މުޙައްމަދު މުނައްވަރު]]

'''Dr. Mohamed Munavvar''' ([[Dhivehi]]: ޑރ. މުޙައްމަދު މުނައްވަރު)was born in the island of [[Meedhoo (Seenu Atoll)]] in [[Maldives]]. He was former Attorney General of [[Maldives]].
==Early and personal life== Born in 1961, Munavvar spent early days of his life at his native island Meedhoo. In 1971 he came to Male' for education. Munavvar married twice and have 2 daughter, one from each of his wives.
==Educational background== Munavvar completed his secondary education in [[English Preparatory and Secondary School]] in Male'. ==Political career== He was former MP of [[Addu]] Atoll constituency. {{start box}}
{{succession box | before=? | title=[[Attorney General of the Maldives]] | years=1993&ndash;2003 | after=[[Hassan Saeed]]}}
{{end box}}
