{{Persondata <!-- Metadata: see [[Wikipedia:Persondata]]. --> | NAME = Munavvar, Mohamed | ALTERNATIVE NAMES = | SHORT DESCRIPTION = | DATE OF BIRTH = | PLACE OF BIRTH = | DATE OF DEATH = | PLACE OF DEATH = }} {{DEFAULTSORT:Munavvar, Mohamed}} [[Category:Maldivian lawyers]] [[Category:Members of the Majlis of the Maldives]] [[Category:Maldivian Muslims]] [[Category:Living people]] [[Category:Attorneys general]] [[Category:Government ministers of the Maldives]] [[Category:Maldivian Democratic Party politicians]] [[Category:People from Malé]] [[Category:Peoples' Friendship University of Russia alumni]] [[Category:Expatriates in the Soviet Union]]
